<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"3512083-4363799481-1000.jpg","path":"0\/1992\/","mime":"image\/jpeg","sizes":"square_small,scale_super,square_medium,scale_small,scale_medium,square_avatar,square_tiny,square_mini,scale_avatar,screen_medium,scale_large,screen_kubrick","caption":null},"background":[]}' />
==Overview== In [[Characters/Liu_Kang|Liu Kang]]'s reset timeline, the [[Concepts/Tarkatan|Tarkatans]] are not a race of people. Tarkat is a contagious disease that mutates anyone who contracts it. At the first sign of becoming a tarkatan, those people are banished to the wastelands of [[Locations/Outworld|Outworld]]. Many have built a colony here is the desert in an attempt to survive. The colony is led by [[Characters/Baraka|Baraka]], who was previously a highly regarded merchant in [[Locations/Sun_Do|Sun Do]].
